---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Holosynthics"
  description="Holosynthics is a new scientific discovery — 56 irreducible elements that compose everything digital. Founded by Yonathan Shalev at Growing Intelligence."
>
  <Nav />

  <main class="about-page">
    <section class="about-hero">
      <h1>About <span class="accent">Holosynthics</span></h1>
      <p>A new scientific discovery. The building blocks of everything digital.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="about-content">

      <section class="vision-section">
        <div class="vision-text">
          <p>Holosynthics is a new scientific discovery.</p>
          <p>56 irreducible elements that compose everything digital. Like Mendeleev's periodic table revealed the building blocks of all matter, Holosynthics reveals the building blocks of all digital matter.</p>
          <p>AI models are the first application. We decomposed 13 model families and found that every one contains the same 56 elements. But the discovery goes far beyond AI — code, data, content, systems — everything digital is built from these 56 elements.</p>
          <p>Growing Intelligence is building a wide range of solutions on this foundation. Probe56 scans and repairs AI models. More applications are coming.</p>
          <p>The vision: Holosynthics becomes the universal language of everything digital. Everything will be measured, understood, and improved through the 56 elements.</p>
          <p>Two papers published on Zenodo. The discovery validated across 13 architecture families. Methods protected by provisional patents filed with the USPTO.</p>
          <p class="world-line">The world is moving to Holosynthics.</p>
          <p class="founder-line">Founded by Yonathan Shalev.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="patents-section">
        <h2>Patents &amp; IP</h2>
        <div class="patents-grid">
          <div class="patent-card">
            <div class="patent-label">Provisional Patent Application</div>
            <h3>Holosynthics Analysis Framework</h3>
            <p>System for identifying and classifying 56 universal element types across AI language models.</p>
            <span class="patent-status">Filed · 2026</span>
          </div>
          <div class="patent-card">
            <div class="patent-label">Provisional Patent Application</div>
            <h3>GI Surgeon — Targeted Model Editing</h3>
            <p>Method for applying precision edits to correct model deficiencies without retraining. Protected by provisional patents filed with the USPTO.</p>
            <span class="patent-status">Filed · 2026</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="papers-quick">
        <h2>Published Research</h2>
        <div class="papers-list">
          <a href="https://zenodo.org/records/19852341" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="paper-link">
            <span class="paper-li-num">Paper I</span>
            <div>
              <div class="paper-li-title">Holosynthics: Element-Level Decomposition of Language Models into 8 Universal Atom Types</div>
              <div class="paper-li-doi">doi:10.5281/zenodo.19852341</div>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a href="https://zenodo.org/records/20736159" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="paper-link">
            <span class="paper-li-num">Paper II</span>
            <div>
              <div class="paper-li-title">The Periodic Table of AI: 56 Universal Elements Across 11 Language Models</div>
              <div class="paper-li-doi">doi:10.5281/zenodo.20736159</div>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="contact-section">
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <div class="contact-box">
          <a href="mailto:yonathan@growing-intelligence.com">yonathan@growing-intelligence.com</a>
          <a href="https://growing-intelligence.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">growing-intelligence.com</a>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page { padding-top: 64px; }

  .about-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 80px 24px 60px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 40% at 50% 0%, rgba(76,201,240,0.1) 0%, transparent 60%);
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 60px);
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .accent { color: var(--cyan); }
  .about-hero p { font-size: 18px; color: var(--muted); }

  .about-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px 80px;
  }

  section { margin-bottom: 72px; }

  h2 {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  /* Vision */
  .vision-text p {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: #94A3B8;
    line-height: 1.85;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .vision-text p:first-child {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #E2E8F0;
  }

  .world-line {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--cyan);
    margin-top: 32px;
  }

  .founder-line {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Patents */
  .patents-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .patent-card {
    background: var(--bg2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 24px;
  }

  .patent-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--pink);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .patent-card h3 {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .patent-card p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #94A3B8;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .patent-status {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--green);
    background: rgba(34,197,94,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.25);
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }

  /* Papers */
  .papers-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }

  .paper-link {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    background: var(--bg2);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .paper-link:hover { border-color: rgba(0,217,255,0.3); text-decoration: none; }

  .paper-li-num {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--pink);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    padding-top: 2px;
  }

  .paper-li-title {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .paper-li-doi {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-family: monospace;
    color: var(--cyan);
  }

  /* Contact */
  .contact-box {
    background: var(--bg2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 28px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .contact-box a {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--cyan);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .contact-box a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .patents-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .vision-text p:first-child { font-size: 18px; }
  }
</style>
